make them look like this." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Richard Tomasian, lamenting the closing of his family's Blvd. Cafe 
hamburger stand in Duarte, which for decades served travelers on Route 66 but 
is being bulldozed to make way for a redevelopment project shopping center. 
</P>
