<HEADLINE>
<P>
ABORTION: 'LONG LINE' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The editorial on abortion was excellent. I sincerely appreciate it. I have been 
waiting and watching for a historical story. 
</P>
<P>
There is so much time, energy and money wasted on fetuses and almost no concern 
or compassion for newborns with AIDS or drug dependencies, or babies lacking 
proper care. 
</P>
<P>
There is much too much preaching instead of support for more facts, more 
knowledge and more education. 
</P>
<P>
MARGARET GARCIA 
</P>
<P>
Homeland 
</P>
</TEXT>
