GALLARDO, MIGUEL ANGEL; DRUG ARRESTS -- MEXICO; DRUG SMUGGLING -- UNITED 
STATES; DRUG SMUGGLING -- MEXICO; DRUG SEIZURES; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- COLOMBIA; 
DRUG SMUGGLING -- COLOMBIA; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- SOUTH AMERICA; DRUG SMUGGLING 
-- SOUTH AMERICA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
