<P>
OIL SPILLS -- ALASKA; HAZARDOUS MATERIALS -- DISPOSAL; EXXON VALDEZ (SHIP); 
SHIP ACCIDENTS -- ALASKA; PRINCE WILLIAM SOUND; GULF OF ALASKA; CONSERVATION; 
POLLUTION CONTROL 
</P>
