<HEADLINE>
<P>
ASIAN APPLIANCE MARKET GROWING, REPORT SAYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
TOKYO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The home appliance market in the newly industrialized economies in Asia grew at 
an annual rate of 19% in the past several years, prompted by accelerating 
horizontal division of labor, an industry report said. 
</P>
<P>
The Japan Electrical Manufacturers' Assn. said the report was based on a survey 
of 10 countries in Asia -- South Korea, Taiwan, Hong Kong, Singapore, China, 
the Philippines, Thailand, Malaysia, Indonesia and India. 
</P>
</TEXT>
