pitch got past catcher D.C. Olsen. ; Photo, Jon Montgomery is congratulated by 
Scott Adams after Montgomery's homer helped Sunny Hills defeat Fullerton. DAVID 
MURONAKA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
